    <div class="content">
      <p class="intro">While it appears as "7o9o," our name is legally composed of the numerals 7 and 9, each followed by the letter 'o.' Yet its true meaning lies in the phrase it evokes: "to go."</p>
      
      <p>This seemingly simple expression embodies a deeper philosophy. It originated from a practical habit—taking leftover food to go—but represents something more fundamental: the principle of thoughtful efficiency. We believe in preserving what has value, in questioning conventions that waste resources, and in making choices that honor both pragmatism and sustainability.</p>
      
      <p class="closing">In a world often bound by superficial etiquette, we champion substance over appearance, utility over waste, and reasoned judgment over thoughtless conformity.</p>
